thread.title: BRIEF-Fujian Raynen Technology to set up embroidery machine computer control system related JV

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Fujian Raynen Technology to set up embroidery machine computer control system related JV

organizations.name: reuters) - fujian raynen technology co ltd

text:
Feb 5(Reuters) - Fujian Raynen Technology Co Ltd
* Says co and partners plan to jointly invest 36 million yuan to set up a JV, which will be mainly engaged in embroidery machine computer control system related business
* Says co will hold 70 percent stake in the JV
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/Bys1NX
